{"word":"G4172 - πόλις - pólis - pol'-is - City","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πόλις</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>pólis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pol'-is"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>City"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"ஊர், நகரம், பட்டணம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. the heavenly Jerusalem"},{"paragraph":"2. the abode of the blessed, in heaven"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably from the same as <a href=\"#/G4171 - πόλεμος - pólemos - pol'-em-os/4171\">G4171</a>, or perhaps from <a href=\"#/G4183 - πολύς - polýs - pol-oos'/4183\">G4183</a>; a <i>town</i> (properly with walls, of greater or less size): - city."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4172 - πόλις - pólis - pol'-is/4172\">G4172</a>, <a href=\"#/G4173 - πολιτάρχης - politárchēs - pol-it-ar'-khace/4173\">G4173</a>, <a href=\"#/G4174 - πολιτεία - politeía - pol-ee-ti'-ah/4174\">G4174</a>, <a href=\"#/G4175 - πολίτευμα - políteuma - pol-it'-yoo-mah/4175\">G4175</a>, <a href=\"#/G4176 - πολιτεύομαι - politeúomai - pol-it-yoo'-om-ahee/4176\">G4176</a>, <a href=\"#/G4177 - πολίτης - polítēs - pol-ee'-tace/4177\">G4177</a>"}]}